    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently well-maintained. Mechanically, it is very sound; the engine runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts reliably, providing a comfortable and confident driving experience. While the exterior and interior show some minor signs of normal use consistent with its age, the car remains clean and presentable. It is a dependable choice for anyone looking for a solid, road-ready vehicle that has many miles left to give.",
      "price": 35000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
